{"tid":1984043,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【721九個月】蔡思貝IG發感言：有些事情不是說忘記就能忘記","createTime":"2020-04-22T08:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T08:10:57.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"df497a54d6e4bf666500e6799f3731bf09167e92","tid":1984043,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T08:05:20.000Z","msg":"去年7月21日元朗黑夜，無警時份發生的白衫人襲擊市民事件，及警方執法態度，掀起社會要求成立「獨立調查委員會」調查箇中問題。警民關係撕裂，令大台一度押後播放劇集《機場特警》，直至最近在疫情下才播，首播當日也惹起不少人表明擺看。<br />\n<br />\n昨日適逢是「721事件」九個月，有份主演《機》劇的蔡思貝在劇集播放後，於IG上載劇照，並貼文「有些事情，不是說放下就能放下，有些經歷，不是說忘記就能忘記」。<br />\n<br />\n這邊廂蔡思貝在IG留言，那邊廂昨晚多名防暴警察晚上在元朗區內巡邏，一度在又新街舉起藍旗警告，以違反限聚令為由票控現場十多人，而九個月前卻一度無影無蹤。思貝留言獲不少網民回應「721 831」、「721 九個月」、「721 不能忘記」及「不會忘記721」等，同時亦有網民為她加油。<br />\n<br />\n至於方丈會如何解讀思貝在「721事件」九個月日子講「不是說放下就能放下」。想知IG貼文另有含意，大家要拭目以待！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200422/large/1587537148_d1c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200422%2Flarge%2F1587537148_d1c0.jpg&h=0f54d98f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200422/large/1587541804_c199.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200422%2Flarge%2F1587541804_c199.jpg&h=583b28ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200422/FLM3IPPD6LKV47SBCYQ4ZII4UI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200422%2FFLM3IPPD6LKV47SBCYQ4ZII4UI%2F&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6ChAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=699af0b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200422%2FFLM3IPPD6LKV47SBCYQ4ZII4UI%2F&h=59aa313f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200422/FLM3IPPD6LKV47SBCYQ4ZII4UI/</a>"},{"pid":"5b122c9f1044e3e5a0ce44f4aff20fe53c90c64f","tid":1984043,"uid":186723,"like":5,"disli